    MaxCoordinateFinder - Class in DetectAdjacentProperties
    Deprecated.
    This class is deprecated and will be removed in a future release. Use CoordinateFinder.findMaxCoordinates(List) instead. This class provides methods to find the maximum coordinates (X and Y) from a list of PropertyPolygon objects. It iterates through the vertices of each property polygon and identifies the highest X and Y values.
